---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import tablet from "../images/svg/tablet.svg";
import check from "../images/svg/check.svg";
import Button from "./Button.astro";
---

<section id="about">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <Image loading="lazy" src={tablet} alt="Tablet" id='tablet' />
    <div class="text">
      <span>THE BOOK</span>
      <h2>About the book</h2>

      <p>
        In this book, we will explore the art and science of landing page
        design. We will delve into the key <br /> elements that make up an effective
        landing page, including copywriting, layout, design, and user
        experience.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <Image loading="lazy" src={check} alt="Check" />
          Ideal for those who are starting now or want to reinforce their knowledge
          in UI;
        </li>
        <li>
          <Image loading="lazy" src={check} alt="Check" />Contains 8 chapters for you to read,
          learn and practice;
        </li>
        <li>
          <Image loading="lazy" src={check} alt="Check" />40 tips with examples to avoid
          interface errors.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <Button>Buy the ebook</Button>
      <Button variant="text">Read a preview</Button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  div.wrapper {
    display: flex;
    gap: 17rem;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  div.text {
    ul {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      gap: 1rem;

      li{
        display: flex;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        align-items: center;
      }
    }

    button:first-of-type{
      margin-right: 2rem;
    }
  }

  img#tablet {
      width:30%;
    }
</style>
